user.canProvide:
I've spent a bunch of time in/around the payments, mobile gaming, restaurant, and venture spaces over the past decade. 

Always happy to chat about whatever's on your mind. :)
user.intro:
Hey Contrarians! I'm Eric, the Founder + Managing Partner of Contrary. 

Prior to starting Contrary six years ago, I was an early employee at a startup called Kamcord, which ultimately got bought by Lyft.

Before that, I was in college, where I first hatched the idea for Contrary while working on a payments startup.
user.lookingFor: Support you all however I possibly can in your careers. :)
